His book, "When Technology
Strikes will help you

00:44:08.080 --> 00:44:10.820 align:middle line:84%
tremendously,
because we don't know

00:44:10.820 --> 00:44:12.240 align:middle line:90%
how long this could happen.

00:44:12.240 --> 00:44:15.850 align:middle line:10%
Could be a day, a
week, a month, a year.

00:44:15.850 --> 00:44:17.690 align:middle line:10%
Protect yourself
and your family.

